code: import{BIDS}from"../../constants";import axios from"@helpers/axios/private.axios";import store from"../../redux/store";export const getOpenedHistory=()=>async dispatch=>{try{const state=store.getState();const walletType=state.wallet.active_wallet.type;dispatch({type:BIDS.HISTORY_REQUEST});const resp=await axios.get("/bid/active/".concat(walletType?walletType:"demo"));dispatch({type:BIDS.CHANGE_OPENED_HISTORY,payload:resp.data.data.bids});dispatch({type:BIDS.HISTORY_LOADED});}catch(e){console.log("ERRROR");}};
